name: Jenna Coleman LoRA
description:
This might be my best profile yet...

A Stable Diffusion LoRA profile based on Jenna Coleman, aka Clara Oswald from Doctor Who.

Place it in "stable-diffusion-webui\extensions\sd-webui-additional-networks\models\lora" folder in Automatic1111 WebUI root folder.

Made using kohya-ss so make sure to have that extension installed!

In txt2img, under "Additional Networks", select "Enable" and under Model 1 select "Jenna Coleman" and assign a weight between 0.3-0.7 (feel free to experiment!). In the prompt text window use "Jenna Coleman" within your prompt to generate images.

Embed has been trained on Stable Diffusion 1.5 model.

I Recommend the model https://civitai.com/models/4922/grapelikedreamfruit - Gives amazing realistic renders.
